                            <comment id="12574843" author="djd" created="Tue, 4 Mar 2008 04:55:10 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Initial patch that adds actions to SystemPermission as described.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;More testing needed but SystemPrivilegesPermssionTest passes with this patch which simply replaces SystemPermssion(&quot;shutdown&quot;) with SystemPermission(&quot;server&quot;, &quot;shutdown&quot;).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;No testing of specific actions has been tried, so the code may be buggy in the way it handles action but wanted to throw the code out there to give others a chance to see the direction.&lt;/p&gt;
</comment>
